    <div id="status-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: American Optometric Association (AOA). Comprehensive adult eye and vision examination. St. Louis (MO): American Optometric Association (AOA); 2005. 37 p. [83 references].</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
    </div>
