 (95677002), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0017601&amp;fLockTerm=Glaucoma">Glaucoma</a>
 (23986001), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0020490&amp;fLockTerm=Hypermetropia">Hypermetropia</a>
 (38101003), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0027092&amp;fLockTerm=Myopia">Myopia</a>
 (57190000), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0200202&amp;fLockTerm=Ocular+motility+study">Ocular motility study</a>
 (17259005), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0030688&amp;fLockTerm=Patient+education">Patient education</a>
 (311401005), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0031061&amp;fLockTerm=Perimetry">Perimetry</a>
