 (252886007), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1719905&amp;fLockTerm=Ultraviolet-absorbing+sunglasses">Ultraviolet-absorbing sunglasses</a>
 (420584006), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0042792&amp;fLockTerm=Vision+screening">Vision screening</a>
 (408760009), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0042812&amp;fLockTerm=Visual+acuity">Visual acuity</a>
 (363983007), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0200150&amp;fLockTerm=Visual+acuity+testing">Visual acuity testing</a>
 (16830007), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0042825&amp;fLockTerm=Visual+field+study">Visual field study</a>
 (86944008), <a href="/web/20180712204814/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0042793&amp;fLockTerm=Visual+testing">Visual testing</a>
